title: Emerson MW9005SS Compact Countertop Microwave Oven with Button Control, LED Display, 900W 5 Power Levels, 6 Auto Menus, Glass Turntable and Child Safe Lock, 0.9 Cu. Ft, Stainless Steel
description: Make your microwave exciting again! The Emerson 0.9 Cu. Ft. Microwave Oven brings speed, power and convenience together in one sleek package. Dinner time just got a whole lot easier. With 900 Watts of power, this microwave speeds up cooking times so you spend less time prepping and more time enjoying delicious meals. The intuitive presets take the guesswork out of heating popular foods, while 5 power levels let you tailor cooking times. The child safety lock provides peace of mind. Make mealtimes fast, easy and safe for the whole family. The Emerson 0.9 Cu. Ft. Microwave Oven for quick and even heating, this powerful microwave will revolutionize the way you cook!
